01:11:24.363 --> 01:11:26.286
Bruce. Bruce, honey.

01:11:26.783 --> 01:11:27.909
What?

01:11:28.409 --> 01:11:32.084
I know I've been acting
a little crazy lately.

01:11:32.163 --> 01:11:35.212
