01:12:06.489 --> 01:12:08.241
Spooked?

01:12:08.324 --> 01:12:10.452
Yeah, at the...

01:12:12.370 --> 01:12:13.667
retirement party.

01:12:13.746 --> 01:12:14.998
You know, I saw...

01:12:15.998 --> 01:12:18.842
