01:12:19.418 --> 01:12:22.718
And I didn't know
who I was anymore.

01:12:23.673 --> 01:12:25.675
Well, what was I gonna do?

01:12:26.175 --> 01:12:27.518
What can I do?

01:12:28.052 --> 01:12:29.395
