we'll survive another one.

01:17:33.607 --> 01:17:35.701
...God.

01:17:39.280 --> 01:17:40.577
God, I...

01:17:41.115 --> 01:17:44.619
I really am gonna miss this. Right?

01:17:44.702 --> 01:17:46.625
Honey.

01:17:57.715 --> 01:17:59.467
- Have a good drive.
- Thanks again.

